PrecisAppointment of the following persons as directors of the board of directors of the Canada Pension Plan Investment Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years. (GAIL COOK-BENNETT, of Etobicoke, Ontario; DALE G. PARKER, of Vancouver, British Columbia; RICHARD THOMSON, of Toronto, Ontario; HONOURABLE GÉRARD V. LA FOREST. of Fredericton, New Brunswick; M. JOSEPH (JOE) REGAN, of Willowdale, Ontario; and DAVID WALKER, of Winnipeg, Manitoba)
